Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's going to be a contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Miki from our class?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She's entering the Junior Design Contest\Nthat the city's putting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to\Nmodel the wedding dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Model? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She said I'm perfect for it.\NI've already gone for the fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just waiting to see\Nthe finished product.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And who's going to be the groom?\NThe Frog Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Frog's Bride
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr., you're always\Nmaking fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, I'm just being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:00:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Takamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Contest in Chaos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you want from me,\NMiss Takamiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.\NI just happen to be going this way, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn. She got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hush, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be quiet in the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got away from Takamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been following me all over\Nthe for place the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?\NShe's very persistent, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,\Nhave you seen Miki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My wedding dress\Nis supposed to be ready today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She... came to see me about that,\Njust a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want\Nto talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone stole the\Ndrawing for my design.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so sorry.\NI have such long legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Suzushiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Suzushiro from Group E.\NWe're competing in the same contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mami Suzushiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NI'm sure that's when it was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always thought\Nof me as a rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If she uses my design in the contest,\Nit'll put me in a difficult position...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,because her presentation\Ncomes before mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki, don't lose faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The right will always be rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... and I was\Nlooking forward to the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, please get\Nher design back for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, I wish I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Miss Takamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,With her following me around,\NI can't turn into St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up hope.\NYou'll think of something, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to wear that wedding dress\Nand model in the contest too! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.\NI'll help you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fix you an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime,\Nyou become St. Tail and get the design.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.\NWhat do you mean by alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you specify the contest's date\Non the challenge to Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"...at the Conversational\NEnglish Seminar..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asuka, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you if you wanted to know\NSt. Tail's identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still harping on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pest.\NI told you what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:05:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who she is!\NI just want to arrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, I won't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior Design Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what Haneoka's\Nbeen worked up about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so great about it, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow,\Nat the Junior Design Contest...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will steal Mami Suzushiro's wedding\Ndress design drawing. -St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew she'd make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That St. Tail...\Nshe's after a wedding dress this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to follow\Nmy own lead this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll soon learn\NSt. Tail's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so cute back then, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you were a bit slimmer, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No magic will bring\Nback the old you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Change back,\Nchange back, change back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or something like that... wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a professional magician.\NThat shouldn't catch you off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I... what's up, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a wedding\Ndress contest tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one of the models.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to get married\None of these days, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early\Nto start getting lonely, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I have to\Nbe St. Tail and a bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to work hard at both!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Ruby, you have to stay home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you,\Nyou better do a good job protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, of course,\Nto some degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean,\N'to some degree'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, St. Tail is sure to appear\Nafter the contest begins. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're positive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's why you\Ncan relax until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they can protect themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Green Room 1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here,\NMiss Takamiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for a phone.\NI have to call Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not wearing an ID tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Only models and contestants are\Nallowed in here. Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sticking to you like glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not moving from that spot,\Nnot for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Seira, are you sure it's all right\Nfor me to participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Mami Suzushiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's definitely the one I designed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let them get away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put on a good show,\Nshall we, Kono?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The city's Junior Design Contest\Nwill soon begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Final preparations are being made.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All contestants,\Nplease assemble on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there as soon as I change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll help her change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamiya, you're welcome to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, gee, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Seira, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:09:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Transforming into\NSt. Tail quietly is so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Seira, you're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I put on the wig and veil,\Neveryone will think it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, and I'm supposed to be a nun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you to put on\Na good act and keep Takamiya here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, be careful too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those two doing in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by your looks\Nyou must be one of the models.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The contest is starting.\NYou'd better change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your dressing room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,W... Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, now's your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I saw a black shadow there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Show's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is going good so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for the hard part.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We will begin the judging at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Entry #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My design!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When is she going to\Nturn into St. Tail, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneoka, don't you have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but my number is last.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Meimi, please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We are experiencing a power failure.\NFor your safety, please remain seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail is here in the hall!\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:14:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!\NHaneoka's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire hall is in an uproar,\Nbut stand by, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew. They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I've got to get this ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, quiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, you have to wear that instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the design.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving this back\Nto the real designer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:14:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there, get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold it! What does she mean,\N'real designer'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is in apology\Nfor causing such a commotion here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bouquets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For the future brides.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bouquets from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I want one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, they're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior Designer Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There, it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly up high.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's heading for the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She got away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now where's she going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Green Room 1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you come back here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Asuka Jr., isn't she beautiful?\NFor goodness sake, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Really very beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your design that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So... So that's what St. Tail was after!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to change the subject.\NHow typical of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,O... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Entry #30, you're up next.\NReport to the stage immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takamiya,\Nyou can go without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And the winning entry in\Nthe Junior Designers Contest is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:18:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,#30, Miki Kono's design!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki, you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A wedding dress sure is mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It even makes Meimi seem different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if she's St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you how you'd feel\Nif she was St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NThat's a really bad joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no joke.\NI'll even make a bet on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Is that why\Nyou've been following her around?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's one of your classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, how about this then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If Meimi isn't St. Tail,\Nthen I'll stop following her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I'm right, you'll have to date me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You promise you'll stop following her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that Meimi is St. Tail.
